### Order API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5132/api/order

### Get all orders
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get a specific order by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### Create a new order
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locationId": 1,
  "orderItems": [
    {
      "itemType": "entree",
      "itemId": 1,
      "quantity": 1,
      "selectedOptions": [1, 2]
    },
    {
      "itemType": "drink",
      "itemId": 1,
      "quantity": 2,
      "selectedOptions": []
    }
  ],
  "customerName": "John Doe",
  "orderNotes": "Extra napkins please"
}
